title: Best Bits of the Week Show with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About The NFL Trivia Trivia with Lunchbox  (Week of 2/1)
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week Show with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About The NFL Trivia Trivia with Lunchbox  (Week of 2/1)
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan2 brings on Lunchbox to talk about the final matchup in NFL Trivia Vs. The Ladies...and he makes a big deal about making it to the no. 1 slot. Scuba Steve comes on to talk about the two dead bodies he found in his house.
